CustomField.description: A number from -1 to 100 (including decimals) that indicates the detailed level of match on the name of the matched candidate. 0 indicates no match. 100 indicates most accurate match. Note: This parameter is not applicable for Multi-Process High-Volume Match.

CustomField.label: D&B Name Match Score
